wiki.content:
"Savin' Me" is a song written by Canadian rock band Nickelback. It was released as the third major single from their fifth album All the Right Reasons (2005). The song reached number two on the Canadian Singles Chart and number nineteen on the U.S. Billboard Hot 100 chart.
